Nearly a century after magic was recognized as a real form of technology, Miyuki Shiba begins her term at Magic High School. An “honor” student, she dreamed of enjoying school with her older brother Tatsuya, an “irregular” student. But a rift between the gifted Course 1 students and the inferior Course 2 students could stand in the way. This time, Miyuki is the star of the show!
(Source: Funimation)
Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken 2nd Season Part 2
The second cour of Tensei Shitara Slime Datta Ken 2nd Season.

This game’s got me obsessed! It’s like it’s taken over my life... wait—HARD MODE ACTIVATED. No-no-no-no-no! It has literally taken me and thrown me into the part of Penelope Eckhart. Love is easy as the heroine, but as the hated villainess, I’m trying very hard not to die… at the hands of my brothers… the prince… a fork… every possible ending is death! This world is stacked against me, but can my wits and insider game knowledge score the affection of these male characters? Or the reset button??? (Source: Tapas)
Totsuide kita Yome Aisouwarai Bakari Shiteru

A Samurai is worried about the fact that his wife always seems to wear a forced smile whenever she's with him. Note: initially self-published on the author's Twitter it later became serialized on Nico Nico Seiga where the story continued.
